title: Couple With Heart Person Woman Medium Skin Tone Dark Skin Tone
alsoKnownAs: Person and Man Holding Hands with Heart
description: Depicts a couple, with a person with a dark skin tone at the center, connected by a heart. It symbolizes love, romance, and partnership.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, the couple emoji featuring a person and a woman with medium and dark skin tones, united by a bright red heart, showcases Apple's commitment to diverse representation and warm design. The figures are rendered with smooth gradients and soft rounded edges, giving them a gentle, approachable feel. This emoji on Apple devices powerfully symbolizes love, partnership, and the beauty of blended relationships.
